te VR app for Oculus headsets. HyperSpace Music revolutionizes your auditory experience by transforming your favorite MP3 tracks into breathtaking visual masterpieces.\n\nSimply load your MP3 files into the default \"music\" folder on your headset, and let HyperSpace Music do the rest. Each song is brought to life through stunning, real-time visualizers that respond dynamically to the beats, rhythms, and melodies of your music. Whether you're grooving to pop, rocking out to metal, or relaxing with classical tunes, HyperSpace Music creates an immersive visual landscape that complements every genre.\n\nDive into a vibrant universe where sound and sight merge, offering an unparalleled sensory adventure. Customize your experience with various visual themes and effects, ensuring that no two journeys are ever the same. HyperSpace Music is perfect for music lovers, VR enthusiasts, and anyone looking to elevate their listening experience.\n\nApp Created by Krish T & Vicente M - Future Productions Films\nVideo Backgrounds - Bj\u00f6rn Richter & TellSoto\nSpace Cover Art - Photo by Felix Mittermeier\n\nLINKS:\nhttp://www.future-productions.co.uk\nhttps://dietechrecruiter.de/author/bj%C3%B6rn-richter/ \nhttps://www.pexels.com/photo/blue-universe-956981/", "short_description": "HyperSpace Music is a VR app for Oculus headsets that lets you discover a new world of music through stunning visualizers. Load your favorite MP3 tracks into the music folder on your headset, and watch as HyperSpace Music transforms each song into an immersive visual experience, with vibrant, dynamic landscapes reacting in real-time to the beats and rhythms of your music."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://future-productions.co.uk/privacy-policy-for-hyperspace-music-vr-application/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Future Productions Films Ltd", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.future-productions.co.uk/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8244448688912468"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1239348220764120"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1239348220764120"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1722399746, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1239348220764120"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9046656968691632", "version": "1.1.3"}, "id": "1845929692484603", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8244448648912472", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9046656968691632"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1845929692484603"}]}, "change_log": "Dear Hyperspace passengers, we have an exciting new update. All the scenes and music flow constantly. Your music is no longer interrupted by switching scenes.\n\nThe fighter movement will change in scene two from month to month to keep things unique.\n\n\nPlease enjoy this update we are busy making more great visuals in the next few weeks.\n\nMany Thanks\nHyperspace Music Team", "created_date": 1729957036, "id": "9046656968691632", "version": "1.1.3", "version_code": 14, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "9046656268691702"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8244448648912472", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9046656968691632"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1845929692484603"}]}, "change_log": "URGENT CRITICAL UPDATE:\n\nDear Hyperspace Travellers,\n\nWelcome back to the journey through the stars! We\u2019ve made three updates today to bring you even more exciting improvements and serious progress in Hyperspace Music.\n\nPlease install this latest update for the best experience.\n\nUpdate Log:\n\nThrusters Upgraded: We've added more intricate details and flames to the starfighter thrusters, bringing more dynamic energy to your hyperspace journey.\n\nStarfighter Formations: Starfighters now fly in tight formation with smoother, more detailed animations, offering a sense of precision and intensity during your missions.\n\nHyperspace Window: The hyperspace window layer has been opened and added, giving you a breathtaking visual experience as you blast through the cosmos.\n\nCinematic Color Correction: We\u2019ve added cinematic color correction to some of the scenes, enhancing the overall visual tone and atmosphere.\n\nPlease note that these changes are temporary. Our team will be pushing the playlist feature in the next update after the 15th, and as a result, this visual work will need to be redone. It may not look quite the same afterward, so enjoy the current enhancements while they last!\n\nWe\u2019re thrilled about the serious progress we've made and what it means for the future of your journey. Stay tuned for more exciting updates!\n\n- The Hyperspace Music Team", "created_date": 1728063472, "id": "8890658077624856", "version": "1.1.2", "version_code": 13, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8890656714291659"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8244448648912472", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9046656968691632"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1845929692484603"}]}, "change_log": "URGENT CRITICAL UPDATE:\n\nDear Hyperspace Travellers,\n\nWelcome back to the journey through the stars! Our latest update brings crucial improvements, fine-tuning your cosmic adventure with exciting new visual enhancements.\n\nUpdate Log:\n\nThrusters Upgraded: We've added more intricate details and flames to the starfighter thrusters, bringing more dynamic energy to your hyperspace journey.\n\nStarfighter Formations: Starfighters now fly in tight formation with smoother, more detailed animations, offering a sense of precision and intensity during your missions.\n\nHyperspace Window: The hyperspace window layer has been opened and added, giving you a breathtaking visual experience as you blast through the cosmos.\n\n(Fixed where scene would not skip on Version 1.1.0)\n\nPlease note that these changes are temporary. Our team will be pushing the playlist feature in the next update after the 15th, and as a result, this visual work will need to be redone. It may not look quite the same afterward, so enjoy the current enhancements while they last!\n\nWe hope you enjoy these latest upgrades. Stay tuned for more exciting updates!\n\n- The Hyperspace Music Team", "created_date": 1728044083, "id": "8888990107791653", "version": "1.1.1", "version_code": 12, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8888988464458484"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8244448648912472", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9046656968691632"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1845929692484603"}]}, "change_log": "Dear Hyperspace Travellers,\n\nWelcome back to the journey through the stars! Our latest update is packed with new visual enhancements to make your cosmic adventure even more exhilarating.\n\nUpdate Log:\n\nThrusters Upgraded: We've added more intricate details and flames to the starfighter thrusters, bringing more dynamic energy to your hyperspace journey.\n\nStarfighter Formations: Starfighters now fly in tight formation with smoother, more detailed animations, offering a sense of precision and intensity during your missions.\n\nHyperspace Window: The hyperspace window layer has been opened and added, giving you a breathtaking visual experience as you blast through the cosmos.\n\nPlease note that these changes are temporary. Our team will be pushing the playlist feature in the next update after the 15th, and as a result, some of this visual work will need to be redone. It may not look quite the same afterward, so enjoy the current enhancements while they last!\n\nWe hope you enjoy these latest upgrades, and stay tuned for more exciting updates!\n\n- The Hyperspace Music Team", "created_date": 1728037363, "id": "8888224391201558", "version": "1.1.0", "version_code": 11, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8888222791201718"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "8244448648912472", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9046656968691632"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1845929692484603"}]}, "change_log": "Dear Hyperspace Travelers,\n\nBuckle up, as we're taking another leap into the cosmos!\n\nWe're excited to announce that the visual experience in Hyperspace Music has improved and will improve further in the next update. \n\nHere's what's new:\n\nResolution Boost: We've started enhancing the overall visual quality! The cockpit resolution has received a notable upgrade, bringing sharper details to your journey through space.\n\nStarfighter Visuals: The starfighter visuals have also been enhanced, delivering even more clarity as you navigate the abstract universe.\n\nUpcoming Features: We're still hard at work on introducing a playlist feature, coming in the next update, so you can fully customize your musical journey!\n\nAs always, we remain dedicated to improving your experience with each update. Stay tuned for more exciting developments.\n\nSee you among the stars!\n\nK - Hyperspace Music", "created_date": 1727864808, "id": "8869363689754295", "version": "1.0.9", "version_code": 10, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "8869362409754423"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}